@host = http://localhost:8080
@adminToken = change-me

### Service info
GET {{host}}/

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Prometheus metrics
GET {{host}}/metrics

### Upsert route with key in URL
# This is the recommended request. The stream key is taken from the URL.
PUT {{host}}/v1/routes/test-key
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "target": "rtmp://localhost:1936/live/test-target"
}

### Create route with key in request body
POST {{host}}/v1/routes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "streamKey": "test-key",
  "target": "rtmp://localhost:1936/live/test-target"
}

### Get route
GET {{host}}/v1/routes/test-key

### List routes
GET {{host}}/v1/routes

### Delete route
DELETE {{host}}/v1/routes/test-key
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### List active RTMP sessions
GET {{host}}/v1/sessions

### Close active RTMP session
# Replace the id before sending.
DELETE {{host}}/v1/sessions/session-id-goes-here
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Invalid stream key example, should return 400
PUT {{host}}/v1/routes/bad/key
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "target": "rtmp://localhost:1936/live/test-target"
}

### Invalid target example, should return 400
PUT {{host}}/v1/routes/bad-target
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "target": "http://localhost/live/test-target"
}
